# Trivy ignore file — intentional dev-environment design decisions
# These findings are acknowledged and accepted for a non-production EKS cluster.
# Equivalent Checkov skips are in .checkov.yml (CKV_AWS_39, CKV_AWS_260).

# EKS public API endpoint is enabled for developer access without VPN.
# Will be restricted to private-only + VPN when promoting to production.
AVD-AWS-0040

# EKS public access CIDR defaults to 0.0.0.0/0.
# Will be scoped to corporate CIDRs in production.
AVD-AWS-0041

# Security group egress allows all outbound traffic to 0.0.0.0/0.
# Standard pattern for EKS worker nodes that need to pull images, reach AWS APIs, etc.
AVD-AWS-0104
